7. AMOSPro Compiler Floppy disc installation.

In order to make some room on your AMOSPro_System disc, the installer
will have to remove some files from it, and copy them onto a newly
formated disc called "AMOSPro_Extras:"

So before proceeding, you should with the Workbench:

- Format a blank disc,

- Make a copy of you current AMOSPro_System disc as a matter of security.

2 boutons:

(1) My discs are ready, proceed with installation

(2) Back to Workbench to format and copy

En bas de l'ecran:

Having trouble? Just read the manual at page XXX where the entiere procedure
is fully described.

Si (2): 
Tu appelle la procedure _BACK_TO_WB. Elle fermera tout les ecrans, liberera
le maximum de memoire, et fera revenir le workbench. Sur le workbench
il y aura une joli icone "BACK TO INSTALLER" sur lequel clicker pour
revenir.
La procedure rouvrira tout avant de revenir.



8. Tu appelle la procedure _FLOPPY_INSTALL et je prend le relai.



